To pair Tilty BT's:
1. AT+ROLE=1 -> OK
---- To scan for devices ----
2. AT+IPSCAN=20,5,20,5 -> OK
3. AT+INQM=1, #of devices to find, timeout in seconds -> discovered devices
4. AT+INQ -> discoverable devices
-------- To connect ---------
5. AT+LINK: device address -> OK (example address: 1234,56,ABCDE)
6. You're connected! There will be a delay 

------ To disconnect --------
7. AT+DISC -> disconnect results
